Subject: Some of the collection tasks were not completed correctly and resulted in improper reports
Description: Transaction (Process ID 86) was deadlocked on lock resources with another process and has been chosen as the deadlock victim. Rerun the transaction. The collection job returned error and subsequent reports generated were not having correct data.
What_We_Know__c:
Customer has a customer "SHELL_ALLUserAccount" activity scan job that is failing with this error:
"Transaction (Process ID 86) was deadlocked on lock resources with another process and has been chosen as the deadlock victim. Rerun the transaction. The collection job returned error and subsequent reports generated were not having correct data."

Customer replied that the error is resolved on its own and activity scan is now running as expected.
Next_Steps__c:
Since error got resolved on its own and activity scan "SHELL_ALLUserAccount" is now running as expected support is waiting for a reply from customer with results. 
Customer will upload logs if issue is still present.
